      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IM DOWNBYTHEBEACH NZ (1) is lightly raced but promising. Raced up to four wide when kicking off in Australia with a win at this circuit and distance two back then did a great job again at his latest appearance at Bendigo, beaten only 1.7 metres into second by a recent Group 2 winner. Should enjoy a nice run from the inside draw and has plenty of upside.  LILLY LOTUS (3) has not raced since she made it three wins on the trot by scoring at Shepparton in the only run of her campaign last July. Very good fresh performer with two wins and two placings from four attempts and was readied with a trial win. INTRUSION (7) has produced two nice efforts from the back row at this venue since recording back-to-back wins. Draws wide but he is going well. HEATSEEKER (8) has decent form and draws for a trail. He could be dangerous.",
